      • USE_EPOLL

        @Deprecated
public static final com.netflix.config.DynamicBooleanProperty USE_EPOLL
        Deprecated. 
        This field is effectively a noop, as Epoll is enabled automatically if available. This can be disabled by using the FORCE_NIO property.

      • defaultOutboundChannelType

        @Deprecated
public static final java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicReference<java.lang.Class<? extends io.netty.channel.Channel>> defaultOutboundChannelType
        Deprecated. 
        This is a hack to expose the channel type to the origin channel. It is NOT API stable and should not be referenced by non-Zuul code.
